001package edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.service;
002
003import edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model.dto.CountryResponse;
004import edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model.dto.LeagueResponse;
005import edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model.dto.TeamResponse;
006import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Single;
007import retrofit2.http.GET;
008import retrofit2.http.Path;
009import retrofit2.http.Query;
010
011/**
012 * Used to get the API key to populate the game with needed information from the API
013 */
014public interface SportsDBProxy {
015
016  @GET("{api_key}/all_countries.php")
017  Single<CountryResponse> getAllCountries(@Path("api_key") String apiKey);
018
019  @GET("{api_key}/all_leagues.php")
020  Single<LeagueResponse> getAllLeagues(@Path("api_key") String apiKey);
021
022  @GET("{api_key}/lookup_all_teams.php")
023  Single<TeamResponse> getAllTeams(@Path("api_key") String apiKey,@Query("id") String leagueId);
024}
